page.title: 20Credits
page.content:
We must thank people for their effort and contributions to our Project. Miss Howlett for her patience and know how on the computer. Then, Mr Jenner, Miss Stevenson, Mrs Humphreys, Miss Pieri and Mrs Kirby for all their encouragement and organization. Last but not least, we must thank all the First Year children (Forms 1.1, 1.2, 1.3, 1.4 and 1.5) of Lothingland Middle School who have helped collect all the information .
We must not forget Somerleyton Primary School who have made some useful contributions. They were encouraged and guided by Mrs Boardman, their headmistress. Mr Sutton (Project Co-ordinator)
